s="margin"><p class="justify"> You can now use the camera´s IP address to access the <a href="/Web_User_Interface/">Web User Interface</a> with your default web browser.</p></div></article></div></div> <% include ../_partials/content/_bluenav-general-mobile.ejs %><footer> <% include ../_partials/amp/_amp-footer.ejs %></footer></body></html>